rabbitmq
  - messaging broker
  - client libraries to connect with broker is available in many languages / frameworks
  
  
Based on AMQP 

plugin based architecture to support STOMP & MQTT

plugins
  - SHOVEL          moving messages from one broker to another
  - FEDERATION      sharing messages between brokers
  - MANAGEMENT      monitoring & controlof brokers and cluster of brokers
  
  
  Sending messages
    1.  Establish connection
    2.  Ensure the receiving queue is available
    3.  Sends the message
    4.  Close the connetion
    
  Receivinng messages
    1.  Receive messages via a callback method 
